'''Ccix Nuredin''', isem-is n tidett, '''Nuredin Mezyan''', d agerruj n yedles azwaw/[[aqbayli]]: d amedyaz, d acennay, d asegbar u d aɣeyyaḍ (musicien). Ilul deg 1918 di taddart Agemun di [[Laṛebɛa n Ayt Yiraten]]. D mmis n Si Muḥand Taḥar Ugemun, i llan d asnelmad di taddart-is, deg aɣerbaz Sidi Abderaḥman. Imut deg 1999, yeǧǧad deffir-is timaḍ (d 100-yat) n izlan, d isefra akw d tuɣac. Afares-is (sa production) i bdat send/zdat (uqbel) n trad umdal amezwaru.

== Tuddert n Ccix Nuredin ==

Alama d 16 isegwasen, Ccix Nuredin i ttruḥu s aɣerbaz n [[Leqran]]. Deg 1935 ikcem ar tɣiwant n Lezzayer tamanaɣt anda yezdeɣ gma-s ɣur i gella. Illa ay 'serbay' deg aṭas n leqhawi d iseččayen. Illa yesɛa yiwen useččay amecṭuḥ 'gargote' di 'Port-Saïd (square Bresson)'. Assegwas seld (1936), illa ay ttɣenni mi ysirid leḥwal, dɣa anemhal n 'Pathé Marconi' Mas 'Finkel' i zedɣen ur ibad ara i syin, i slay-as i ṣut-is. Inna yas ma yebɣa ad isekles deg uxxam uzawan n 'Pathé Marconi', ansuf yis-ek. Imiren, i sufɣed i tikkelt tamezwarut tuɣac ines i yettwasnen 'Anef-iyi ad ruɣ', akw d 'A xali xali'.

Sin issegwasen send (1938), isekles adebsi amezwaru ines, anda llant azal n 12 n tezlatin. Garasent:
'Alu Tsisiti', 'Yellis n tmurt', 'Anef-iyi ad ruɣ', 'A xali xali', atg. Uri ɛeṭerl ara armi id isbed 
ayen umi neqqar 'orchestre' aɣerfan aqbayli amezwaru, netta d : Namus, Sidaḥ, Aḥmed Meǧul, Ḥaǧ Menwar. D nitni iǧan i waṭas n izuren ad ufraren, am: Kamal Ḥemadi, Yusef Abǧawi, Racid Mezyan, atg.

Deg 1960, yura yiwen n wedlis umi isemma 'Un Algérien raconte' ar Tizrigin 'Seuil'. Deg 1998, Amyaru aqbayli Yusef Nasib yerra yas tajmilt di yiwen n wedlis s wazal-is anda id yeḥka tameddurt-is u yura-d ugar n 200 isefra ines. Adlis aki ifeɣ-d ar Tizrigin 'El-Ouns', isem-is 'Ccix Nuredin: Aẓruf, Amedyaz, Acenay', neɣ s tefranṣiṣt : 'Cheikh Noureddine, comédien, poète, chanteur'.

== Talalit n Rradyu n teqbaylit ==

Deg 1938, Ccix Nuredin d netta i yellan deffir n tlalit n Rradyu n [[teqbaylit]] igellan di 'rue du Dr Saâdane (ex-Berthèzene)'. Tuɣal tin umi neqqar tura Amaṭṭaf wis 2 n Rradyu taɣelnayt n [[Dzayer|Lezzayer]]. Illa ixedem degs aṭas umezgun, rwayat 'sketč', akw d tuɣac d tedwilin. Rrayu aki, tella d ttin ansi id tefɣent tinazurin timuqranin, am : Lla Zina, Lla Yamina, Nna Crifa, Ǧamila, atg.

Ccix Nuredin isekles ugar n 500 tezlatin. Illa iḥemel azawan aɣerfan neɣ ayen umi neqqar 'Caɛbi'. Dɣa d netta i yuran unazzur n 'Caɛbi' Ḥaǧ Mrizeq, taɣuct ig ttwasnen imiren ilmen d tarbaɛt n takurt uḍar: 'Mouloudia d’Alger'. Illa i msuder (coyoyer) netta d inazuren imuqranen am : Ccix Lɛemqa, Muqran Agawa, d Sadeq Abǧawi, atg. Axedmen yakw tuɣac i Rradyu n teqbaylit i waken attidir. Daɣen Ccix Nuredin ixedem aṭas n tcequfin umezgun i Rradyu n Teqbaylit, anda i tturar d acḥal issegwasen tamtilt n yiwet n ṭmeṭṭut “Xalti Aduda”, zdat inazuren wiyaḍ am: Muḥamed Ḥilmi, Amar u Yaqub, Saɛid Zanun, Ali Abdun, Saɛid Ḥilmi, Aḥmed Aymen, atg.

Ccix Nuredin ixdem daɣen aṭas n tedwilin i rradyu n teqbaylit. Garrasent id yefɣen deg 1956, illan ilmend iccenayen deg ubrid ulemed neɣ 'Chanteurs amateurs'. Dɣa n nnuba yaki i yuɣalen ar zdat tettwasen s yisem : Icennayen uzeka.

== Ccix Nuredin d Sinima ==

Ccix Nuredin illa daɣen d asegbar muqwren n Sinima. Amseḍru isura n Sinima i yettwasnen: Moḥamed Laxdar Ḥamina, iḥemel-it nezzeh. Dɣa ifek yas tamtilt deg usaru: 'Chronique des années de braise' ig bwin yiwen n warraz di 'Cannes' deg 1975. Di 1983, ifek yas daɣen tamtilt deg usaru : Tugna Tannegarut (La dernière image).

Ger isura wiyaḍ anda isɛa tamtilt, d wigi:

: ''Les hors-la-loi'' n Tufik Fares deg 1968, 
: ''Patrouille à l’est'' n Amar Laskri deg 1970,
: ''Tahia ya Didou'' n Moḥamed Zinet deg 1973. 
: ''Elise ou la vraie vie'' n 'Michel Drach' deg 1974, akw d 'Marie-José Nat' d Muḥamed Cwix
: ''El Chebka'' n ɣwati Bendeduc deg 1976, 
: ''Chant d’automne'' n Meziyan Yala deg 1982, akw d Rwiced d Ḥasan Lḥasani.

Llan daɣen sin usura 'Les Enfants de Novembre' d 'les Chevaux du soleil' ig ttwaxedmen di tmurt n Sbanyul akw ttnazurt n cnna taqbaylit Ḥnifa, ad fellas yilu isuref. Asaru yaki n 'les Chevaux du soleil' iḥekud tuddert n 'Lmuqrani', ar tura ur d yurar ara di Lezzayer.

== Timlilit d Sliman Ɛazem ==

Deg 1972 Ccix Nuredin yunag ar [[Paris]] di [[Fransa]], anda yemlal d unazur [[Sliman Ɛazem]], u bdan amecwar n ccna di sin d acḥal isegwasen. Skelsen azal n 96 n tezlatin, garasent tid n teḍṣa d necraḥa. Dɣa d anecta iǧan deg 1981 Ccix Nuredin megdul seg umuɣ/amulas n warazen ilmend n wid iqedcen i yedles azzayri. Tagi d yiwet ger tuɣac icnan di sin : Ccix Nuredin d Sliman Ɛazem.

